===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# the [[reappearance]] of an [[ancestral]] [[characteristic]] in an [[organism]] after several [[generation]]s of [[absence]]. Often also refered to as a [[throwback]].
# the recurrence or reversion to a past [[behaviour]], [[method]], [[characteristic]] or [[style]] after a long period of absence.

